</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:23pt;text-indent:-69.9pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 100.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:-4.41;mso-layout-grid-align:none;mso-para-margin-left:2.98gd;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:23pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">（先进单位和第五批对口定点扶贫挂职干部先进个人拟定说明）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:23pt;text-indent:-69.9pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 100.75pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:-4.41;mso-layout-grid-align:none;mso-para-margin-left:2.98gd;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">一、评选范围<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">在川委办<span lang=\"EN-US\">[2012]12</span>号安排的<span lang=\"EN-US\">239</span>个单位中产生。<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>市和成都市的<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>区（县）统一列入评选范围。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">二、先进名额<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">按照昌平常委和曲木史哈副省长批示同意的《关于开展<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年度对口定点扶贫扶贫工作总结暨第六批扶贫挂职干部选派工作方案》，对口定点扶贫先进单位<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>个，第五批对口定点扶贫挂职干部先进个人<span lang=\"EN-US\">35</span>名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">三、确定先进候选名单的原则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">为确保此次先进表扬工作公正、公平、公开，先进名单的确定遵守：不突破已定名额，需经市（州）推荐，兼顾先进单位和先进个人的平衡。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正黑体简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">四、先进单位候选名单的确定<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:31.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">各地上报的先进单位名单共<span lang=\"EN-US\">65</span>个。采纳<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个牵头部门提出的意见，省“四大班子”和<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个对口定点扶贫牵头部门保留为候选名单；参与对口扶贫工作的<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>个市和成都市的<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>个区县中考虑<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个（原拟全部进行表扬，考虑到如果全部表扬，占比较大，且只有甘孜州推荐了<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>','新增工作计划','2014-07-07 17:18:14','11','12');
