p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\">法规处<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2014.7.24</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\"><o:p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22pt;font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-bidi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-hansi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">四川省扶贫和移民工作局<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22pt;font-family:方正小标宋简体;letter-spacing:-1pt;mso-bidi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-hansi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;\">2014</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:22pt;font-family:方正小标宋简体;letter-spacing:-1pt;mso-bidi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-hansi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;\">年全省扶贫移民重点工作</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22pt;font-family:方正小标宋简体;letter-spacing:-1pt;mso-bidi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-hansi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;\">新闻宣传实施方案<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22pt;font-family:方正小标宋简体;letter-spacing:-1pt;mso-bidi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;mso-hansi-font-family:方正小标宋简体;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">（初稿）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" align=\"center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">为切实加强我省扶贫移民新闻宣传工作，扩大影响力，提升美誉度，按照</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">月</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">11</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">日省委宣传部召开的“四川发展重点工作宣传报道协调推进会议”的总体部署，现结合实际，制定此实施方案。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;\">一、宣传重点<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:楷体;\">（一）扶贫开发机制改革创新方面</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、开展贫困识别、建档立卡的创新性做法，推进精准扶贫的探索与实践，贫困群众参与扶贫项目建设的基层创造。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进干部驻村帮扶工作的进展与做法。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进贫困县考核、约束、退出机制建设的政策举措。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">4</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进“四到县”制度的政策措施与基层实践。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:楷体;\">（二）“四大片区”内外扶贫攻坚的成效与经验<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore;\">1、</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">大小凉山彝区扶贫攻坚，突出宣传“十项扶贫工程”实施情况及成效。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、我省高原藏区扶贫攻坚，以“六项民生工程”为重点，特别突出“扶贫解困行动计划”。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进扶贫新村建设的成效与做法。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">4</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进旅游扶贫试点的成效与做法。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、推进产业扶贫的成效与做法，突出扶贫特色产业园区建设。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\">6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、培育雨露计划、扶贫小额贷款、易地扶贫搬迁“三大扶贫品牌”的措施与成效。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:楷体;\">（三）社会力量参与扶贫开发</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、全国扶贫济困日宣传活动，重点宣传“结对认亲、爱心帮扶”活动开展情况及经验总结推广。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:30pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、中央机关在川定点扶贫和东西扶贫协作